Package entity.Appointments

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
entity.Appointments.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
Represents an appointment within the system. Stores details such as the appointment ID, patient, doctor, date, time, and type. Provides methods to manage and retrieve appointment information.
